Before editing, here is the implementation shape: bounded GET probes to `/v1/models` for OpenAI-compatible/llama.cpp and `/api/tags` for Ollama, returning `{ ok, reachable, ... }` results instead of throwing. Failures will use stable error codes for invalid config, HTTP errors, network failures, malformed JSON/shape, and timeout.
